@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="what-we-buy-content">
    <div class="what-we-buy-container">
        <span style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--primaryColor)">Privacy Policy</span> <br />
        <span style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #8195a4;">
            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>When you visit our website, register, or place an order, we may collect personal details such as your name, email address, mailing address, phone number, and other relevant information to enhance your experience.</p>


            <h2>Use of Collected Information</h2>
            <p>The information we collect may be used to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Personalize your experience and tailor content to your preferences</li>
                <li>Improve our website’s functionality and services</li>
                <li>Respond to customer service inquiries effectively</li>
                <li>Process transactions securely and efficiently</li>
                <li>Send periodic emails about orders, promotions, or other relevant updates</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Data Security Measures</h2>
            <p>We prioritize your data security by implementing the following measures:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Regular security scans for vulnerabilities</li>
                <li>Malware scanning</li>
                <li>Secured networks with restricted access to authorized personnel</li>
                <li>Encryption of sensitive data via Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology</li>
                <li>Secure payment processing through trusted third-party providers</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
            <p>Our website uses cookies to enhance user experience and gather analytics. Cookies enable us to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Remember user preferences for future visits</li>
                <li>Track advertisements and website interactions</li>
                <li>Improve site performance and functionality</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Users can adjust browser settings to disable cookies, though this may impact some website features.</p>

            <h2>Third-Party Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We do not sell or share personal data with third parties. Users may request data deletion at any time by submitting a request via our opt-out form.</p>

            <h2>Google Services</h2>
            <p>While we have not enabled Google AdSense, we may implement it in the future. Google's advertising policies ensure a positive user experience and comply with industry standards.</p>

            <h2>Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA)</h2>
            <p>We do not knowingly market to or collect personal information from children under 13, in compliance with COPPA regulations.</p>

            <h2>Fair Information Practices</h2>
            <p>In the event of a data breach, we will notify affected users via email and website notification within 31 business days. We adhere to the principle of individual redress, ensuring users have enforceable rights against data processors who fail to comply with privacy laws.</p>

            <h2>CAN-SPAM Compliance</h2>
            <p>We comply with the CAN-SPAM Act by:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Using accurate subject lines and sender information</li>
                <li>Identifying promotional emails clearly</li>
                <li>Providing an option to unsubscribe from email communications</li>
                <li>Processing unsubscribe requests promptly</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you wish to stop receiving emails, follow the instructions at the bottom of our emails, or contact us at <a href="mailto:info@usamericareteststrips.com">info@usamericareteststrips.com</a>.</p>

            <h2>Contact Information</h2>
            <p>For any privacy-related inquiries, please contact us at:</p>
            <p>(917) 203-8615</p>
        </span>
    </div>

</div>